Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.29,0:01:04.75,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(422,482)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:01:03.12,0:01:04.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,数数我的钱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.12,0:01:04.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Counting me money
Dialogue: 1,0:01:04.95,0:01:06.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,钱比蜜糖还要甜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.95,0:01:06.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,money sweeter than honey
Dialogue: 1,0:01:06.97,0:01:08.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,钱钱这个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.97,0:01:08.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Money, money this
Dialogue: 1,0:01:08.20,0:01:09.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,钱钱那个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.20,0:01:09.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Money, money that
Dialogue: 1,0:01:09.07,0:01:11.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,利润养肥我钱包
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.07,0:01:11.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Profit will make me wallet fat
Dialogue: 1,0:01:11.33,0:01:12.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.33,0:01:12.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What
Dialogue: 1,0:01:12.22,0:01:14.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上个月利润降了三块钱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.22,0:01:14.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Profit's down $3 from last month
Dialogue: 1,0:01:14.72,0:01:16.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得加倍严格控制才行了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.72,0:01:16.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got to start running a tighter ship around here
Dialogue: 1,0:01:17.40,0:01:19.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感谢选择蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.40,0:01:19.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you for choosing the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:01:19.53,0:01:20.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是找你的零钱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.53,0:01:20.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's your change
Dialogue: 1,0:01:20.73,0:01:22.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥先生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.73,0:01:22.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:22.27,0:01:22.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.27,0:01:22.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:22.82,0:01:26.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,刚说的那堆找钱胡话是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.82,0:01:26.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's with all this change nonsense?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:26.11,0:01:28.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,绕上去再绕下来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.11,0:01:28.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Over and under
Dialogue: 1,0:01:28.26,0:01:30.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抓住末端  穿过去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.26,0:01:30.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Grab the end, put it through here
Dialogue: 1,0:01:30.42,0:01:32.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,往上绕过喇叭口
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.42,0:01:32.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,up and around, round the horn
Dialogue: 1,0:01:32.20,0:01:33.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,系紧完工
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.20,0:01:33.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,bring it back home
Dialogue: 1,0:01:34.63,0:01:35.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.63,0:01:35.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spongebob
Dialogue: 1,0:01:35.37,0:01:37.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,付你工资不是雇你来玩扮装游戏的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.37,0:01:37.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I ain't paying you to play dress up
Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.95,0:01:41.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要呼吸到你休息时间吸去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.95,0:01:41.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Breathe on your own time
Dialogue: 1,0:01:41.70,0:01:43.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,付你工资不是雇你来呼吸的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.70,0:01:43.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't pay you to breathe
Dialogue: 1,0:01:43.54,0:01:45.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你完全没付我们工资
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.54,0:01:45.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You hardly pay us at all
Dialogue: 1,0:01:46.60,0:01:47.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.60,0:01:47.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That reminds me
Dialogue: 1,0:01:48.23,0:01:49.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有样东西要给你们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.23,0:01:49.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got something for you
Dialogue: 1,0:01:51.50,0:01:52.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.50,0:01:52.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:01:52.22,0:01:54.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,少得可怜的补偿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.22,0:01:54.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Our meagre restitution
Dialogue: 1,0:01:56.98,0:01:59.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,发薪日甜美的香气
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.98,0:01:59.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The sweet smell of payday
Dialogue: 1,0:02:01.95,0:02:02.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.95,0:02:02.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:02:02.65,0:02:03.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是我准备干洗的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.65,0:02:03.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's me dry cleaning
Dialogue: 1,0:02:03.85,0:02:05.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是你的票子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.85,0:02:05.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's your check
Dialogue: 1,0:02:05.69,0:02:07.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是你的  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.69,0:02:07.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and here's yours, Spongebob
Dialogue: 1,0:02:07.80,0:02:10.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的钱我不能收下  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.80,0:02:10.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't accept your money, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:02:10.67,0:02:13.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我热爱煎肉饼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.67,0:02:13.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Grilling is my passion
Dialogue: 1,0:02:13.02,0:02:14.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.02,0:02:14.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.82,0:02:18.57,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1080,316)}账单
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.82,0:02:18.57,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(338,284)}呼吸 说话 站立 存在\N浪费时间 咀嚼
Dialogue: 1,0:02:14.82,0:02:18.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就是站在收银台都得付钱给你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.82,0:02:18.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're making me pay you to stand at the cash register?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:18.57,0:02:20.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.57,0:02:20.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:20.05,0:02:21.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你发什么神经
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.05,0:02:21.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have you gone off the deep end?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.12,0:02:24.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这里得做出一点改变
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.12,0:02:24.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's going to be a few changes around here
Dialogue: 1,0:02:24.52,0:02:27.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要每次逮到你们两个在偷懒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.52,0:02:27.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Every time I catch you two goofing off
Dialogue: 1,0:02:27.22,0:02:29.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就要罚你们钱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.22,0:02:29.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going to charge you for it
Dialogue: 1,0:02:29.26,0:02:30.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,18
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.26,0:02:30.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,18
Dialogue: 1,0:02:30.16,0:02:31.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,19
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.16,0:02:31.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,19
Dialogue: 1,0:02:31.05,0:02:32.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有20
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.05,0:02:32.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and 20
Dialogue: 1,0:02:32.25,0:02:33.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拿去吧  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.25,0:02:33.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here you go, Mr. K
Dialogue: 1,0:02:33.37,0:02:35.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这么多钱应该够缴清我的冒失行为了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.37,0:02:35.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think this should cover all my nonsense
Dialogue: 1,0:02:35.84,0:02:37.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再给五毛钱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.84,0:02:37.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And here's an extra 50 cents
Dialogue: 1,0:02:37.06,0:02:38.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,作为我还系了鞋带的罚款
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.06,0:02:38.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for when I was tying my shoe
Dialogue: 1,0:02:39.79,0:02:42.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你这是在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.79,0:02:42.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spongebob, what do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:42.87,0:02:45.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只是在缴清我欠蟹老板的钱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.87,0:02:45.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm just giving Mr. Krabs the money I owe him
Dialogue: 1,0:02:45.01,0:02:49.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一分钱都不给那个小气螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.01,0:02:49.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well I am not paying that cheapskate Krabs one cent
Dialogue: 1,0:02:49.20,0:02:51.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,建议你也照着我做
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.20,0:02:51.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I suggest you do the same
Dialogue: 1,0:02:51.07,0:02:52.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.07,0:02:52.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:52.11,0:02:54.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们工人必须联合起来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.11,0:02:54.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We've got to unite as workers
Dialogue: 1,0:02:54.33,0:02:57.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要求老板给予我们应得的尊重
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.33,0:02:57.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and demand the respect we deserve from the boss
Dialogue: 1,0:02:57.22,0:03:01.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,其实  我跟你应该罢工
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.22,0:03:01.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In fact, you and I should go on strike
Dialogue: 1,0:03:02.41,0:03:04.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我跟你要罢工
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.41,0:03:04.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You and me go on strike?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:04.08,0:03:04.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.08,0:03:04.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure
Dialogue: 1,0:03:04.80,0:03:07.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,毕竟你也很喜欢你的工作  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.80,0:03:07.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,After all you like your job, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:07.05,0:03:07.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.05,0:03:07.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right
Dialogue: 1,0:03:07.69,0:03:09.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你想一直在这工作下去  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.69,0:03:09.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And you want to keep working here, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.93,0:03:10.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.93,0:03:10.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right
Dialogue: 1,0:03:10.55,0:03:11.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且工作期间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.55,0:03:11.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And while you work here
Dialogue: 1,0:03:11.71,0:03:14.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还希望得到公正对待  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.71,0:03:14.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you expect to be treated fairly, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:14.03,0:03:14.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.03,0:03:14.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right
Dialogue: 1,0:03:14.69,0:03:16.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就一起来罢工
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.69,0:03:16.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then let's go on strike
Dialogue: 1,0:03:17.24,0:03:18.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,罢工
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.24,0:03:18.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A strike
Dialogue: 1,0:03:18.34,0:03:21.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要罢工了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.34,0:03:21.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're going on strike
Dialogue: 1,0:03:21.74,0:03:23.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虽然不知道罢工什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.74,0:03:23.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I still don't know what strike means
Dialogue: 1,0:03:23.21,0:03:25.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但我们要罢工了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.21,0:03:25.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But we're going on a strike
Dialogue: 1,0:03:26.77,0:03:28.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你猜怎么着  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.77,0:03:28.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Guess what, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:03:28.12,0:03:30.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我跟章鱼哥要罢工了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.12,0:03:30.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me and Squidward are going to go on strike
Dialogue: 1,0:03:30.56,0:03:31.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,罢工
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.56,0:03:31.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A strike?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:31.60,0:03:32.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.60,0:03:32.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:03:32.50,0:03:34.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你意思是说你们要做抗议标语牌吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.50,0:03:34.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You mean you're going to make picket signs?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:34.32,0:03:35.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.32,0:03:35.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:03:35.15,0:03:37.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还要做抗议演讲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.15,0:03:37.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And you're going to make protest speeches?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:37.35,0:03:38.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.35,0:03:38.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:03:38.32,0:03:41.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且还要求我得尊重你们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.32,0:03:41.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And you're going to demand me respect?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:41.02,0:03:42.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.02,0:03:42.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:03:43.14,0:03:47.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不  不
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.14,0:03:47.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No-no
Dialogue: 1,0:03:47.24,0:03:50.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  你不早说我会被开除
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.24,0:03:50.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, you didn't tell me I was going to get fired
Dialogue: 1,0:03:50.91,0:03:52.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有蟹堡王了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.91,0:03:52.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Without the Krusty Krab--
Dialogue: 1,0:03:52.39,0:03:52.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.39,0:03:52.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I--
Dialogue: 1,0:03:53.06,0:03:53.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.06,0:03:53.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I--
Dialogue: 1,0:03:55.04,0:03:56.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.04,0:03:56.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:03:56.23,0:03:57.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你能抱抱我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.23,0:03:57.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Could you hold me?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:58.47,0:04:01.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我感觉不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.47,0:04:01.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think I'm going be sick
Dialogue: 1,0:04:02.08,0:04:03.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.08,0:04:03.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spongebob
Dialogue: 1,0:04:04.54,0:04:06.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,告诉你个消息  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.54,0:04:06.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Newsflash, Spongebob
Dialogue: 1,0:04:06.17,0:04:07.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也被开除了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.17,0:04:07.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got fired too
Dialogue: 1,0:04:10.01,0:04:13.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以我们才要罢工
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.01,0:04:13.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is exactly why we need to go on strike
Dialogue: 1,0:04:15.68,0:04:17.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他再也不能这么对待我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.68,0:04:17.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He can't treat us like this anymore
Dialogue: 1,0:04:18.15,0:04:22.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他还欠我们一切无法挽回的珍贵时光
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.15,0:04:22.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He owes us for all the precious irretrievable moments
Dialogue: 1,0:04:22.17,0:04:24.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,浪费进了这个垃圾堆里的时光
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.17,0:04:24.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we've wasted in this trash heap
Dialogue: 1,0:04:24.61,0:04:26.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不久他就会发现
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.61,0:04:26.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Soon he'll realise
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.61,0:04:29.20,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1150,376)}招聘
Dialogue: 1,0:04:26.60,0:04:29.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他需要我们  胜过我们需要他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.60,0:04:29.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,he needs us more than we need him
Dialogue: 1,0:04:29.75,0:04:31.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们是团结的工人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.75,0:04:31.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We are workers united
Dialogue: 1,0:04:36.70,0:04:37.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.70,0:04:37.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:04:37.96,0:04:40.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,照着我说的做  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.96,0:04:40.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just do exactly as I say, Spongebob
Dialogue: 1,0:04:40.53,0:04:41.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不久之后
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.53,0:04:41.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and in no time
Dialogue: 1,0:04:41.96,0:04:45.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不仅能重新上岗  还能获得更多
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.96,0:04:45.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you will have your job back, and more
Dialogue: 1,0:04:45.15,0:04:46.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,获得更多
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.15,0:04:46.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And more?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:49.41,0:04:51.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了海绵宝宝  听好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.41,0:04:51.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right Spongebob, now listen up
Dialogue: 1,0:04:51.10,0:04:52.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要教你罢工
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.10,0:04:52.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going to have to teach you how to strike
Dialogue: 1,0:04:53.25,0:04:55.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,首先  先扔掉我们的制服
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.25,0:04:55.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,First, we must get rid of our uniforms
Dialogue: 1,0:04:55.75,0:04:57.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是压迫的象征
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.75,0:04:57.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They are a symbol of our oppression
Dialogue: 1,0:04:57.95,0:05:00.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要你把你帽子扔到地上去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.95,0:05:00.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want you to throw your hat on the ground
Dialogue: 1,0:05:00.72,0:05:01.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.72,0:05:01.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,like so
Dialogue: 1,0:05:01.60,0:05:04.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在踩个稀巴烂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.60,0:05:04.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, stomp it into the dust
Dialogue: 1,0:05:04.45,0:05:05.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到你了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.45,0:05:05.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your turn, Spongebob
Dialogue: 1,0:05:07.37,0:05:08.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就对了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.37,0:05:08.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's the idea
Dialogue: 1,0:05:09.40,0:05:11.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快扔到地上去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.40,0:05:11.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now throw it on the ground
Dialogue: 1,0:05:21.42,0:05:23.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我做不到  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.42,0:05:23.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't do it, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.84,0:05:25.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这顶帽子是我朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.84,0:05:25.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This hat is my friend
Dialogue: 1,0:05:25.35,0:05:26.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从来没压迫过我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.35,0:05:26.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It never oppressed me
Dialogue: 1,0:05:26.97,0:05:29.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你太可悲了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.97,0:05:29.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spongebob, you're pathetic
Dialogue: 1,0:05:29.45,0:05:30.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.45,0:05:30.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look
Dialogue: 1,0:05:30.10,0:05:31.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我把帽子扔到地上了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.10,0:05:31.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I threw my hat on the ground
Dialogue: 1,0:05:32.51,0:05:33.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不打自招
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.51,0:05:33.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A confession
Dialogue: 1,0:05:33.62,0:05:36.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下次三思而扔垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.62,0:05:36.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Next time think before you litter
Dialogue: 1,0:05:37.92,0:05:38.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.92,0:05:38.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 1,0:05:38.67,0:05:39.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝注意听
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.67,0:05:39.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pay attention Spongebob
Dialogue: 1,0:05:39.90,0:05:42.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们现在要做抗议标语牌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.90,0:05:42.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now we're going to make picket signs
Dialogue: 1,0:05:42.00,0:05:44.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是罢工最重要的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.00,0:05:44.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is a very important part of striking
Dialogue: 1,0:05:44.69,0:05:45.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样行吗  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.69,0:05:45.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Like this, Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:45.90,0:05:48.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是栅栏  白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.90,0:05:48.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not A picket fence, you ding-dong
Dialogue: 1,0:05:48.15,0:05:49.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是标语牌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.15,0:05:49.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Picket sign
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.15,0:05:49.37,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(712,920)}抠 鼻
Dialogue: 1,0:05:49.37,0:05:50.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.37,0:05:50.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How's this?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:50.97,0:05:52.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.97,0:05:52.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:05:52.35,0:05:54.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这才是抗议标语牌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.35,0:05:54.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is a picket sign
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.58,0:05:56.96,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(418,234)}蟹堡王不公正
Dialogue: 1,0:05:54.37,0:05:55.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王不公正
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.37,0:05:55.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krusty Krab Unfair
Dialogue: 1,0:05:55.83,0:05:56.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,短小精悍  直击重点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.83,0:05:56.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Short, sweet and to the point
Dialogue: 1,0:05:56.96,0:05:58.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样呢  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.96,0:05:58.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How about this, Squidward?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.75,0:05:58.83,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1002,602)}蟹堡王狂欢会
Dialogue: 1,0:05:59.10,0:06:01.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  是不公正
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.10,0:06:01.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spongebob, it's unfair
Dialogue: 1,0:06:01.03,0:06:02.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是狂欢会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.03,0:06:02.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,not fun fair
Dialogue: 1,0:06:02.70,0:06:03.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,狂欢会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.70,0:06:03.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A fun fair?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:03.75,0:06:04.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.75,0:06:04.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:04.50,0:06:06.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我很想去狂欢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.50,0:06:06.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I could go for some fun
Dialogue: 1,0:06:06.02,0:06:07.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就在蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.02,0:06:07.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,At the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:06:07.94,0:06:09.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.94,0:06:09.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey everybody
Dialogue: 1,0:06:09.14,0:06:10.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一起去狂欢会狂欢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.14,0:06:10.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's go to the fun fair
Dialogue: 1,0:06:16.25,0:06:17.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不公正的蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.25,0:06:17.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krusty Krab is unfair
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.98,0:06:19.77,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1132,144)}不公正
Dialogue: 1,0:06:18.15,0:06:19.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,里面藏着蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.15,0:06:19.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs is in there
Dialogue: 1,0:06:19.92,0:06:21.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小破店里无情站
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.92,0:06:21.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Standing at the concession
Dialogue: 1,0:06:21.50,0:06:23.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,密谋压迫不一般
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.50,0:06:23.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,plotting his oppression
Dialogue: 1,0:06:23.05,0:06:24.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.05,0:06:24.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the heck does that mean?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:24.67,0:06:25.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.67,0:06:25.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know
Dialogue: 1,0:06:25.40,0:06:27.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥要我对大家喊的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.40,0:06:27.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward told me to yell it at people
Dialogue: 1,0:06:27.15,0:06:31.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你一定就是海绵宝宝了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.15,0:06:31.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then you must be Spongebob Squarepants
Dialogue: 1,0:06:31.45,0:06:32.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.45,0:06:32.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:06:32.05,0:06:34.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,兄弟  你就是厨师界的传奇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.05,0:06:34.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dude, you are like a fry cook legend
Dialogue: 1,0:06:34.93,0:06:36.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能在我锅铲上面签名吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.93,0:06:36.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Will you sign my spatula?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:36.77,0:06:38.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能给有志气的厨师做什么都行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.77,0:06:38.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Anything for an aspiring fry cook
Dialogue: 1,0:06:38.75,0:06:40.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请问你是来帮忙罢工的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.75,0:06:40.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, did you come down to help out the cause?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:40.67,0:06:41.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.67,0:06:41.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:06:41.17,0:06:42.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是来抢你饭碗的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.17,0:06:42.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I came to take your job
Dialogue: 1,0:06:43.72,0:06:45.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.72,0:06:45.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks dude
Dialogue: 1,0:06:46.16,0:06:48.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请注意  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.16,0:06:48.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Attention Spongebob
Dialogue: 1,0:06:48.52,0:06:52.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你罢工水平太烂了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.52,0:06:52.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You are a terrible striker
Dialogue: 1,0:06:52.25,0:06:53.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你让你的继任者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.25,0:06:53.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You just let your replacement
Dialogue: 1,0:06:53.95,0:06:55.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,越过了我们罢工的铜墙铁壁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.95,0:06:55.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,cross our picket line
Dialogue: 1,0:06:55.13,0:06:57.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完全没有要挟他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.13,0:06:57.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,without so much as a single threat
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.55,0:06:59.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不起  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.55,0:06:59.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:06:59.00,0:07:00.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要不我再试试标语牌法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.00,0:07:00.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How about I try the signs again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.39,0:07:01.73,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1160,372)}我爱\N蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:07:01.70,0:07:04.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别管标语牌了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.70,0:07:04.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Forget the signs
Dialogue: 1,0:07:04.12,0:07:06.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有事要让你做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.12,0:07:06.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got something for you to do
Dialogue: 1,0:07:06.17,0:07:07.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,站到那边去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.17,0:07:07.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go stand over there
Dialogue: 1,0:07:07.70,0:07:08.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样吗  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.70,0:07:08.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Like this, Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:08.80,0:07:09.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.80,0:07:09.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Almost
Dialogue: 1,0:07:09.92,0:07:13.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再往右边一点  完美
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.92,0:07:13.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A little more to the right, and perfect
Dialogue: 1,0:07:14.20,0:07:16.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,裤头村的居民们  请注意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.20,0:07:16.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Attention people of Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:07:16.70,0:07:20.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们大家都被欺骗了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.70,0:07:20.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You have been cheated and lied to
Dialogue: 1,0:07:20.04,0:07:21.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.04,0:07:21.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I knew it
Dialogue: 1,0:07:22.15,0:07:24.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,温和的劳动者再也不能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.15,0:07:24.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The gentle labourer shall no longer
Dialogue: 1,0:07:24.62,0:07:27.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,遭到蟹老板贪财黑心的大肆伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.62,0:07:27.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,suffer from the noxious greed of Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:07:27.51,0:07:29.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那家伙在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.51,0:07:29.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's that guy talking about?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:29.37,0:07:30.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.37,0:07:30.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know
Dialogue: 1,0:07:30.04,0:07:31.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过他手上有个喇叭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.04,0:07:31.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But he's got a megaphone
Dialogue: 1,0:07:31.35,0:07:34.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要拆开压迫的木板
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.35,0:07:34.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We will dismantle oppression board by board
Dialogue: 1,0:07:34.92,0:07:37.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把大企业的根基锯成两半
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.92,0:07:37.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll saw the foundation of big business in half
Dialogue: 1,0:07:38.15,0:07:42.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,即便需要一辈子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.15,0:07:42.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,even if it takes an eternity
Dialogue: 1,0:07:42.02,0:07:44.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不知道章鱼哥是在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.02,0:07:44.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gee, I don't know what Squidward's talking about
Dialogue: 1,0:07:44.52,0:07:45.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过感觉挺有道理
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.52,0:07:45.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But he sure sounds convincing
Dialogue: 1,0:07:45.97,0:07:47.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有了你的支持
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.97,0:07:47.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,With your support
Dialogue: 1,0:07:47.35,0:07:49.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们会让人民意志的铁锤
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.35,0:07:49.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we will send the hammer of the people's will
Dialogue: 1,0:07:49.89,0:07:55.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,砸穿蟹老板奴役之家的窗户
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.89,0:07:51.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,crashing through the windows
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.32,0:07:55.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of Mr. Krabs' house of servitude
Dialogue: 1,0:07:59.80,0:08:02.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,支持这么久都让我饿坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.80,0:08:02.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All this supporting is making me hungry
Dialogue: 1,0:08:02.55,0:08:05.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家去买蟹黄堡来吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.55,0:08:05.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey everybody, let's go get a Krabby patty
Dialogue: 1,0:08:09.42,0:08:12.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没人在乎劳动者的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.42,0:08:12.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nobody gives a care about the fate of labour
Dialogue: 1,0:08:12.07,0:08:14.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能立刻得到满足就让他们全跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.07,0:08:14.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,as long as they can get their instant gratification
Dialogue: 1,0:08:15.19,0:08:16.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,讲得真好  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.19,0:08:16.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was a great speech, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:08:16.30,0:08:18.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你都快让大家全听你的了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.30,0:08:18.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You practically had them eating out of your hands
Dialogue: 1,0:08:18.42,0:08:21.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然而并没有  对吧章鱼哥先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.42,0:08:21.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But they didn't, did they, Mr. Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:21.81,0:08:24.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那群看客都忙着听我的了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.81,0:08:24.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Because they were too busy eating out of mine
Dialogue: 1,0:08:24.52,0:08:26.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真希望你们两个能早点罢工
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.52,0:08:26.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wish you two would had gone on strike earlier
Dialogue: 1,0:08:26.87,0:08:29.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢你吸引顾客来花钱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.87,0:08:29.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks for attracting all these paying customers
Dialogue: 1,0:08:29.37,0:08:32.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拿标牌加喊口号可太能引流了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.37,0:08:32.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with all your signage and your sloganeering
Dialogue: 1,0:08:32.80,0:08:34.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.80,0:08:34.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:08:34.61,0:08:36.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这次太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.61,0:08:36.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You've gone too far this time
Dialogue: 1,0:08:36.28,0:08:37.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虽然你可以欺辱我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.28,0:08:37.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can pick on me
Dialogue: 1,0:08:37.80,0:08:39.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但章鱼哥是伟大领袖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.80,0:08:39.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but Squidward is a great leader
Dialogue: 1,0:08:39.95,0:08:41.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们是团结的工人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.95,0:08:41.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We are workers united
Dialogue: 1,0:08:41.90,0:08:44.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们已经受够了你的贪财黑心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.90,0:08:44.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're tired of your smelly greed
Dialogue: 1,0:08:44.10,0:08:46.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要锯开你的桌子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.10,0:08:46.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And we're going to saw your tables
Dialogue: 1,0:08:46.07,0:08:48.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用人民的铁锤砸烂东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.07,0:08:48.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and we're going to smash stuff with the people's hammer
Dialogue: 1,0:08:48.71,0:08:49.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.71,0:08:49.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And we're going to--
Dialogue: 1,0:08:50.27,0:08:51.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.27,0:08:51.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're going to--
Dialogue: 1,0:08:52.27,0:08:53.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  另外那段是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.27,0:08:53.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, what was that other part?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:54.19,0:08:56.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要拆开你的压迫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.19,0:08:56.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dismantle your oppressive establishment?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:56.85,0:08:57.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.85,0:08:57.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:08:57.42,0:08:58.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.42,0:08:58.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That too
Dialogue: 1,0:08:59.05,0:09:01.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我跟章鱼哥要一直罢工下去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.05,0:09:01.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And me and Squidward are going to stay on strike
Dialogue: 1,0:09:01.60,0:09:03.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没收到应得的  就绝不罢休
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.60,0:09:03.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,until we get what we deserve
Dialogue: 1,0:09:03.77,0:09:07.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,即便得罢工到永远
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.77,0:09:07.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Even if it takes forever
Dialogue: 1,0:09:07.60,0:09:09.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,永远
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.60,0:09:09.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Forever
Dialogue: 1,0:09:09.97,0:09:15.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,永远
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.97,0:09:15.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Forever
Dialogue: 1,0:09:15.75,0:09:21.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟海绵宝宝罢工到永远
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.75,0:09:21.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,On strike with Spongebob forever
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.99,0:09:30.63,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(314,224)}蟹堡王\N还是不公正
Dialogue: 1,0:09:22.28,0:09:25.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  蟹老头肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.28,0:09:25.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey Squidward, I bet old man Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:09:25.52,0:09:27.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,会在将来某天破产
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.52,0:09:27.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is going to break any day
Dialogue: 1,0:09:27.82,0:09:29.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.82,0:09:29.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:29.42,0:09:38.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对吧  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.42,0:09:38.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:40.34,0:09:43.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得去求蟹老板要回原先的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.34,0:09:43.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got to beg Mr. Krabs for my job back
Dialogue: 1,0:09:43.02,0:09:45.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,了结这场噩梦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.02,0:09:45.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and put an end to this nightmare
Dialogue: 1,0:09:48.57,0:09:50.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚上好  章鱼哥先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.57,0:09:50.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Evening, Mr. Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:09:50.93,0:09:52.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我刚路过这附近
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.93,0:09:52.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was just in the neighbourhood
Dialogue: 1,0:09:52.30,0:09:53.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.30,0:09:53.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I uh--
Dialogue: 1,0:09:53.85,0:09:58.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就想顺道过来求你回来上班
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.85,0:09:58.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,thought I'd drop by to beg you to come back to work
Dialogue: 1,0:09:58.07,0:10:00.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王就快垮了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.07,0:10:00.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Krusty Krab is a wreck
Dialogue: 1,0:10:00.58,0:10:03.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有你和那个黄色小子  我快完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.58,0:10:03.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ruined without you and then that little yellow guy
Dialogue: 1,0:10:03.17,0:10:05.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我雇的青少年把蟹堡王快搞垮了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.17,0:10:05.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The teenagers I hired is ruining the place
Dialogue: 1,0:10:05.60,0:10:06.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最糟糕的就是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.60,0:10:06.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And the worst part is--
Dialogue: 1,0:10:06.95,0:10:09.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们就是缠着我不放
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.95,0:10:09.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,they won't leave me alone
Dialogue: 1,0:10:09.60,0:10:12.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好棒  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.60,0:10:12.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:10:12.62,0:10:14.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,懂我意思了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.62,0:10:14.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See what I mean
Dialogue: 1,0:10:14.02,0:10:18.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  拜托你回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.02,0:10:18.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, please you gotta come back
Dialogue: 1,0:10:18.27,0:10:20.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们想要的你都会给吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.27,0:10:20.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll give us anything we want?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:20.90,0:10:22.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  都会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.90,0:10:22.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, anything
Dialogue: 1,0:10:22.56,0:10:24.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,意下如何  章鱼哥先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.56,0:10:24.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So what do you say, Mr. Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:24.90,0:10:28.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的遭遇让我心如刀绞  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.90,0:10:28.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your story breaks my heart, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:10:28.67,0:10:30.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不然我们就散散步  一起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.67,0:10:30.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why don't we take a little walk and uh--
Dialogue: 1,0:10:30.85,0:10:32.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,讨论我的条件
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.85,0:10:32.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,discuss my terms
Dialogue: 1,0:10:33.24,0:10:36.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的钱包有种不祥的预感
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.24,0:10:36.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got a bad feeling in the pit of me wallet
Dialogue: 1,0:10:36.82,0:10:39.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万恶的黑心老板
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.82,0:10:39.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, mean Mr. Bossman
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.03,0:10:51.83,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1246,300)}罢工
Dialogue: 1,0:10:39.31,0:10:41.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这工作我再也不干
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.31,0:10:41.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm quitting this here job
Dialogue: 1,0:10:41.04,0:10:43.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟章鱼哥罢工真是太兴奋了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.04,0:10:43.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gee, being on strike with Squidward sure is a kick
Dialogue: 1,0:10:43.95,0:10:46.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥的话语依然在我耳边萦绕着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.95,0:10:46.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward's words are still buzzing around in my head
Dialogue: 1,0:10:46.70,0:10:47.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,宛如愤怒水母在飞舞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.70,0:10:47.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,like an angry jellyfish
Dialogue: 1,0:10:47.97,0:10:49.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.97,0:10:49.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward was right
Dialogue: 1,0:10:49.05,0:10:50.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不能光坐这儿不动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.05,0:10:50.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't just sit here
Dialogue: 1,0:10:50.46,0:10:51.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要来行动了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.46,0:10:51.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's time for action
Dialogue: 1,0:10:56.28,0:10:59.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要恢复劳动人民应有的荣耀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.28,0:10:59.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I will restore the working man to his rightful glory
Dialogue: 1,0:11:00.14,0:11:05.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要拆开这蟹堡王压迫的木板
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.14,0:11:01.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I will dismantle
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.34,0:11:05.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,this oppressive establishment board by board
Dialogue: 1,0:11:05.30,0:11:08.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要把这专制的桌子锯成两半
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.30,0:11:08.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I will saw the tables of tyranny in half
Dialogue: 1,0:11:08.64,0:11:11.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咀嚼大企业的脚踝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.64,0:11:11.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gnaw at the ankles of big business
Dialogue: 1,0:11:13.95,0:11:16.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥会特别骄傲的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.95,0:11:16.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward will be so proud
Dialogue: 1,0:11:16.95,0:11:20.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  谈判可真是激烈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.95,0:11:20.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well Squidward, those were intense negotiations
Dialogue: 1,0:11:21.12,0:11:24.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很高兴你能换位思考  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.12,0:11:24.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you saw it our way, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:11:24.52,0:11:26.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在我能开除那群青少年
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.52,0:11:26.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now I can fire them teenagers
Dialogue: 1,0:11:26.65,0:11:29.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把我的两位好小子召回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.65,0:11:29.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and get me two golden boys back
Dialogue: 1,0:11:30.31,0:11:31.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上班时间见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.31,0:11:31.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, see you at work
Dialogue: 1,0:11:37.64,0:11:38.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.64,0:11:38.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sponge--
Dialogue: 1,0:11:38.75,0:11:42.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你都干了什么好事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.75,0:11:42.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spongebob, what have you done
Dialogue: 1,0:11:42.36,0:11:44.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我完完全全照你说的做了  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.36,0:11:44.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I did exactly as you said, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:11:44.37,0:11:46.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我拆了蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.37,0:11:46.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I dismantled the establishment
Dialogue: 1,0:11:46.20,0:11:48.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在工作肯定能要回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.20,0:11:48.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now we'll get our jobs back for sure
Dialogue: 1,0:12:04.37,0:12:06.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.37,0:12:06.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:12:06.55,0:12:08.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.55,0:12:08.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spongebob
Dialogue: 1,0:12:08.87,0:12:11.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么事  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.87,0:12:11.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:11.37,0:12:13.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.37,0:12:13.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here it comes
Dialogue: 1,0:12:13.04,0:12:16.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为了赔偿这些损失
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.04,0:12:16.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In order to pay off these damages
Dialogue: 1,0:12:16.32,0:12:22.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们两个要为我工作  一辈子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.32,0:12:22.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you two are going to work for me forever
Dialogue: 1,0:12:23.91,0:12:25.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,罢工成功了  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.91,0:12:25.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The strike worked Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:12:25.72,0:12:27.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们的工作回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.72,0:12:27.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We got our jobs back
Dialogue: 1,0:12:27.17,0:12:28.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,永远
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.17,0:12:28.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Forever
Dialogue: 1,0:12:28.40,0:12:29.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,永远
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.40,0:12:29.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Forever
Dialogue: 1,0:12:29.56,0:12:31.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,永远
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.56,0:12:31.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Forever
Dialogue: 1,0:12:31.99,0:12:34.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,一辈子后
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.78,0:12:42.28,起司 特殊标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(313,394)}海绵宝宝\N{\fs30} \N{\fs150}珊迪和虫子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.36,0:12:47.07,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1096,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.36,0:12:44.49,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz19\pos(326,458)}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.82,0:12:47.07,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(404,294)\frz21.5}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.41,0:12:49.87,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz18.95\pos(318,318)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.41,0:12:49.87,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz21.2\pos(508,666)}创意总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.41,0:12:49.87,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1034.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 1,0:12:50.18,0:12:53.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啊  裤头村又一个祥和的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.18,0:12:53.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ah, another peaceful evening in Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:12:53.80,0:12:56.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,聆听这一热带海域的寂静
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.80,0:12:56.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Listen to the tropical tranquility
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.50,0:12:59.17,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1092,622)}裤头村
Dialogue: 1,0:13:29.92,0:13:31.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请来两大勺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.92,0:13:31.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Two scoops, please
Dialogue: 1,0:13:31.69,0:13:32.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.69,0:13:32.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 1,0:13:38.04,0:13:39.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,零钱不用找了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.04,0:13:39.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You keep the change
Dialogue: 1,0:13:40.83,0:13:41.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.83,0:13:41.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.01,0:13:52.01,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(186,366)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:13:50.50,0:13:52.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.50,0:13:52.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I saw it
Dialogue: 1,0:13:52.15,0:13:53.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,特别大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.15,0:13:53.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It was big
Dialogue: 1,0:13:53.47,0:13:55.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,扭来扭去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.47,0:13:55.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It was all wiggly
Dialogue: 1,0:13:55.95,0:13:57.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把东西全吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.95,0:13:57.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And it ate everything
Dialogue: 1,0:13:58.15,0:13:59.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.15,0:13:59.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's horrible
Dialogue: 1,0:14:01.98,0:14:06.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是一只阿拉斯加牛虫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.98,0:14:06.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It was an Alaskan Bull Worm
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.32,0:14:04.49,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(712,178)}阿拉斯加
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.49,0:14:05.15,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(712,178)}牛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.15,0:14:06.57,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(712,178)}虫
Dialogue: 1,0:14:11.15,0:14:12.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它吃了我的独轮车
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.15,0:14:12.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He ate my wheelbarrow
Dialogue: 1,0:14:12.82,0:14:15.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它吃了我家小孩的作业
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.82,0:14:15.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He ate my children's homework
Dialogue: 1,0:14:16.12,0:14:18.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都这样了还有必要说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.12,0:14:18.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do I need to say it?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:18.00,0:14:20.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么办才能自保
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.00,0:14:20.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How can we protect ourselves?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:20.42,0:14:21.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.42,0:14:21.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got it
Dialogue: 1,0:14:22.74,0:14:25.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,买个蟹黄堡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.74,0:14:25.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's all buy a Krabby patty
Dialogue: 1,0:14:26.91,0:14:28.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,应该要把大门锁紧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.91,0:14:28.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We should lock our doors
Dialogue: 1,0:14:29.05,0:14:31.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,应该要打电话找我外甥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.05,0:14:31.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We should call my nephew
Dialogue: 1,0:14:31.45,0:14:33.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,应该要挖护城河
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.45,0:14:33.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We should dig a mote
Dialogue: 1,0:14:33.39,0:14:35.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,应该要带走裤头村
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.39,0:14:35.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We should take Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:14:35.77,0:14:38.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,推到别处去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.77,0:14:38.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and push it somewhere else
Dialogue: 1,0:14:40.25,0:14:43.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那办法可能太疯狂了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.25,0:14:43.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That idea may just be crazy enough--
Dialogue: 1,0:14:44.15,0:14:45.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,狂得能害死大家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.15,0:14:45.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to get us all killed
Dialogue: 1,0:14:49.05,0:14:51.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,找个谁去追踪它
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.05,0:14:51.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's get someone to go after it
Dialogue: 1,0:14:51.60,0:14:53.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有谁会傻到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.60,0:14:53.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There ain't no one fool enough
Dialogue: 1,0:14:53.15,0:14:55.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去对付阿拉斯加牛虫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.15,0:14:55.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to take on an Alaskan bull worm
Dialogue: 1,0:15:04.33,0:15:06.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这边有厕所吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.33,0:15:06.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You got a bathroom in this place?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:07.12,0:15:07.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在后面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.12,0:15:07.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In the back
Dialogue: 1,0:15:07.92,0:15:09.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.92,0:15:09.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks
Dialogue: 1,0:15:09.65,0:15:12.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可以帮你们抓虫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.65,0:15:12.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll get your worm for ya
Dialogue: 1,0:15:12.72,0:15:15.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,前提是愿意提供报酬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.72,0:15:15.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that is if you're willing to pay
Dialogue: 1,0:15:15.32,0:15:16.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.32,0:15:16.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:15:16.90,0:15:19.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你一分钱也休想找我要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.90,0:15:19.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll never get a cent out of me
Dialogue: 1,0:15:19.89,0:15:21.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,休想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.89,0:15:21.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Never
Dialogue: 1,0:15:21.35,0:15:24.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我宁愿那条虫马上就进来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.35,0:15:24.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd rather that worm come in here right now
Dialogue: 1,0:15:24.44,0:15:27.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,生吃了你们大家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.44,0:15:27.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and eat you all alive
Dialogue: 1,0:15:34.55,0:15:35.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.55,0:15:35.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:15:36.71,0:15:37.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,讨厌啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.71,0:15:37.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aw shucks
Dialogue: 1,0:15:37.72,0:15:39.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才不要你的钱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.72,0:15:39.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't want your money
Dialogue: 1,0:15:39.10,0:15:41.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,单纯渲染一下气氛而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.10,0:15:41.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was just playing up the drama of the moment is all
Dialogue: 1,0:15:45.84,0:15:46.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.84,0:15:46.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nope
Dialogue: 1,0:15:46.48,0:15:49.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我之所以要平白无故解决掉那条虫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.48,0:15:49.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna take that spineless critter down for nothing
Dialogue: 1,0:15:49.21,0:15:51.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是因为这是私人恩怨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.21,0:15:51.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Because this is personal
Dialogue: 1,0:15:51.69,0:15:53.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看  我尾巴不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.69,0:15:53.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, my tail's gone
Dialogue: 1,0:15:54.86,0:15:58.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那害虫一定在我背后偷袭了  胆小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.86,0:15:55.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Varmit must have got it
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.97,0:15:58.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,while I had my back turned, the coward
Dialogue: 1,0:16:01.32,0:16:03.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要夺回属于我的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.32,0:16:03.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am gonna get back what's mine
Dialogue: 1,0:16:06.50,0:16:07.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.50,0:16:07.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What
Dialogue: 1,0:16:07.55,0:16:09.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是珊迪  你不知道你的对手是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.55,0:16:09.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But Sandy, you don't know what you're up against
Dialogue: 1,0:16:09.90,0:16:14.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们说的可是阿拉斯加牛虫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.90,0:16:14.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We are talking about an alaskan bull worm
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.53,0:16:12.57,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(712,178)}阿拉斯加
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.57,0:16:13.20,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(712,178)}牛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.20,0:16:14.41,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(712,178)}虫
Dialogue: 1,0:16:14.41,0:16:16.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虽然我不了解阿拉斯加
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.41,0:16:16.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well I don't know nothing about Alaska
Dialogue: 1,0:16:16.57,0:16:17.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但是你看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.57,0:16:17.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but lookie here
Dialogue: 1,0:16:18.39,0:16:20.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在我德克萨斯老家  我套过牛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.39,0:16:20.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Back in Texas, I wrangled bulls
Dialogue: 1,0:16:20.75,0:16:22.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也套过虫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.75,0:16:22.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I wrangled worms
Dialogue: 1,0:16:22.46,0:16:23.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在我看来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.46,0:16:23.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,As far as I'm concerned
Dialogue: 1,0:16:23.75,0:16:25.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,牛和虫一起套完全就是省了一条绳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.75,0:16:25.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,doing them both together just saves rope
Dialogue: 1,0:16:25.70,0:16:29.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在我要去把虫子打得落花流水了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.70,0:16:29.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now I'm gonna go kick me some worm tail
Dialogue: 1,0:16:30.58,0:16:31.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是珊迪  你不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.58,0:16:31.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But Sandy, you don't know
Dialogue: 1,0:16:32.12,0:16:33.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放心好了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.12,0:16:33.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Spongebob
Dialogue: 1,0:16:33.90,0:16:34.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不会耗太久的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.90,0:16:34.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I won't be long
Dialogue: 1,0:16:35.11,0:16:35.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.11,0:16:35.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:16:36.24,0:16:36.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.24,0:16:36.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:16:37.05,0:16:38.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快去抓它  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.05,0:16:38.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go get him Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:16:38.22,0:16:40.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们对你信心满满
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.22,0:16:40.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We have the utmost confidence in you
Dialogue: 1,0:16:42.07,0:16:43.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,刚刚你想到了什么办法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.07,0:16:43.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now what was that idea of yours?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:43.85,0:16:45.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,推
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.85,0:16:45.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Push
Dialogue: 1,0:16:48.83,0:16:49.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.83,0:16:49.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:16:49.93,0:16:50.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.93,0:16:50.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:16:50.55,0:16:52.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  是要来看戏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.55,0:16:52.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey Spongebob, you coming to watch?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:52.57,0:16:53.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.57,0:16:53.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:16:53.81,0:16:54.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.81,0:16:54.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't go
Dialogue: 1,0:16:54.95,0:16:55.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.95,0:16:55.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:55.77,0:16:57.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪  我看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.77,0:16:57.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy I saw it
Dialogue: 1,0:16:57.45,0:16:59.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它又大又可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.45,0:16:59.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's big, scary
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.78,0:16:58.66,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(722,106)}大
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.66,0:16:59.53,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(722,228)}可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.53,0:17:00.62,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(782,552)}粉红
Dialogue: 1,0:16:59.53,0:17:00.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还粉红
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.53,0:17:00.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and pink
Dialogue: 1,0:17:01.00,0:17:02.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星的肚脐眼也这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.00,0:17:02.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So's Patrick's belly button
Dialogue: 1,0:17:02.48,0:17:03.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那玩意我也不怕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.48,0:17:03.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I ain't afraid of that neither
Dialogue: 1,0:17:04.12,0:17:06.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它会把你打败的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.12,0:17:06.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll get massacred
Dialogue: 1,0:17:06.02,0:17:07.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  我可是德克萨斯松鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.02,0:17:07.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spongebob, I'm from Texas
Dialogue: 1,0:17:08.10,0:17:10.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你眼中的大  跟我眼中的大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.10,0:17:10.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What you think is big and what I think is big
Dialogue: 1,0:17:10.60,0:17:12.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,根本是两种完全不同的大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.60,0:17:12.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,are two totally different bigs
Dialogue: 1,0:17:12.35,0:17:14.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,并且它抢了我的尾巴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.35,0:17:14.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Besides, he's got my tail
Dialogue: 1,0:17:14.20,0:17:15.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,绝对不能坐视不管
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.20,0:17:15.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't take that sitting down
Dialogue: 1,0:17:15.72,0:17:16.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.72,0:17:16.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 1,0:17:16.51,0:17:16.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.51,0:17:16.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But--
Dialogue: 1,0:17:17.17,0:17:19.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万一抢你尾巴的不是那条虫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.17,0:17:19.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,what if the worm didn't take your tail?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:19.67,0:17:21.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是抢我尾巴的不是虫  那是谁干的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.67,0:17:21.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If that worm ain't got my tail, who does?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:22.95,0:17:23.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.95,0:17:23.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I do
Dialogue: 1,0:17:23.67,0:17:24.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.67,0:17:24.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You do?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:24.27,0:17:24.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.27,0:17:24.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:25.72,0:17:26.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我口袋里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.72,0:17:26.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In my pocket
Dialogue: 1,0:17:28.01,0:17:29.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你怎么不早说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.01,0:17:29.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well why didn't you just say so?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:29.59,0:17:30.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快拿来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.59,0:17:30.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give it here
Dialogue: 1,0:17:31.13,0:17:31.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.13,0:17:31.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on
Dialogue: 1,0:17:36.38,0:17:38.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  那是一根回形针
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.38,0:17:38.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spongebob, that's a paperclip
Dialogue: 1,0:17:38.30,0:17:39.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有一条线头
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.30,0:17:39.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and a piece of string
Dialogue: 1,0:17:39.52,0:17:40.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.52,0:17:40.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No it's not
Dialogue: 1,0:17:40.47,0:17:41.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是你的尾巴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.47,0:17:41.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is your tail
Dialogue: 1,0:17:41.67,0:17:42.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.67,0:17:42.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spongebob
Dialogue: 1,0:17:42.72,0:17:43.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你凭什么知道那不是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.72,0:17:43.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How would you know?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:43.79,0:17:45.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,尾巴在后面根本看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.79,0:17:45.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's always behind you
Dialogue: 1,0:17:46.30,0:17:47.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.30,0:17:47.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't go
Dialogue: 1,0:17:47.29,0:17:50.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.29,0:17:50.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't go
Dialogue: 1,0:17:50.56,0:17:53.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你有什么毛病
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.56,0:17:53.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spongebob, what is the matter with you?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:53.25,0:17:56.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要去给那条没腿的坏蛋来点教训
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.25,0:17:56.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now I'm gonna go give that legless rascal what for
Dialogue: 1,0:17:56.50,0:17:58.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不管你说什么都阻止不了我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.50,0:17:58.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And there ain't nothing you can say to stop me
Dialogue: 1,0:17:58.77,0:18:00.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是吗  那我就说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.77,0:18:00.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, what if I said
Dialogue: 1,0:18:01.65,0:18:03.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,板腊根付地甭侬吸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.65,0:18:03.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Blaggenfidibblenohip
Dialogue: 1,0:18:04.04,0:18:06.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不得不承认  确实拖了我一点时间
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.04,0:18:06.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I gotta admit that's slowing me down
Dialogue: 1,0:18:06.47,0:18:09.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但我还是要去找它
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.47,0:18:09.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I'm still going for him
Dialogue: 1,0:18:09.10,0:18:11.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,尾巴也没大家说得那么值
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.10,0:18:11.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know, tails are so overrated
Dialogue: 1,0:18:11.40,0:18:13.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别想尾巴的事情了  回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.40,0:18:13.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's just forget about it and go home
Dialogue: 1,0:18:13.05,0:18:17.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有果仁冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.05,0:18:17.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got ice cream with nuts
Dialogue: 1,0:18:17.80,0:18:20.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪  我是你爹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.80,0:18:20.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy, this is your Pappy speaking
Dialogue: 1,0:18:20.07,0:18:22.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要禁止你去追踪这条虫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.07,0:18:22.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I forbid you to go after this worm
Dialogue: 1,0:18:22.15,0:18:23.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你给我回来  大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.15,0:18:23.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Y'all come back here, young lady
Dialogue: 1,0:18:23.90,0:18:25.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你又不是我爹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.90,0:18:25.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You ain't my pa
Dialogue: 1,0:18:25.52,0:18:27.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪  要想去找虫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.52,0:18:27.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy, if you want to get to that worm
Dialogue: 1,0:18:27.93,0:18:29.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,必须先过我这关
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.93,0:18:29.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you're going to have to go through me
Dialogue: 1,0:18:34.00,0:18:35.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪  不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.00,0:18:35.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy, no
Dialogue: 1,0:18:35.95,0:18:37.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不能让你走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.95,0:18:37.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can let you
Dialogue: 1,0:18:37.30,0:18:39.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不能让你没命
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.30,0:18:39.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to let you get killed
Dialogue: 1,0:18:39.27,0:18:41.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要是真找到了  它肯定会吃掉你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.27,0:18:41.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you find him you'll get eaten for sure
Dialogue: 1,0:18:41.67,0:18:44.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,某些海里的笨虫子绝对不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.67,0:18:44.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ain't no way some dumb old sea worm
Dialogue: 1,0:18:44.10,0:18:45.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,会吃掉我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.10,0:18:45.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is going to make a meal a me
Dialogue: 1,0:18:45.47,0:18:47.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我德克萨斯来的  可强了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.47,0:18:47.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am too Texas tough
Dialogue: 1,0:18:48.20,0:18:49.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.20,0:18:49.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No-no
Dialogue: 1,0:18:49.27,0:18:50.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你还不够强
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.27,0:18:50.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,not tough enough
Dialogue: 1,0:18:51.08,0:18:53.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你还不够强
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.08,0:18:53.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not tough enough
Dialogue: 1,0:18:53.32,0:18:55.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  别瞎操心了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.32,0:18:55.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spongebob, quit your worrying
Dialogue: 1,0:18:55.05,0:18:56.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我能管好我自己的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.05,0:18:56.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can take care of myself
Dialogue: 1,0:18:56.42,0:18:59.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,毕竟谁是裤头村最强壮的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.42,0:18:59.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,After all, who's the strongest critter in Bikini Bottom?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:03.41,0:19:04.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.41,0:19:04.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You are
Dialogue: 1,0:19:04.12,0:19:05.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是谁最会
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.12,0:19:05.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And who put the
Dialogue: 1,0:19:07.20,0:19:08.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打空手道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.20,0:19:08.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,K in Karate?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:08.72,0:19:09.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.72,0:19:09.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You did
Dialogue: 1,0:19:10.05,0:19:12.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是谁常常保住了你的黄屁股
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.05,0:19:12.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And who saves your yellow backside
Dialogue: 1,0:19:12.92,0:19:14.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,每次都不让它摔坏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.92,0:19:14.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,from certain destruction on a regular basis?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.92,0:19:17.13,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(262,776)}珊迪所有
Dialogue: 1,0:19:16.31,0:19:17.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.31,0:19:17.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You do
Dialogue: 1,0:19:17.32,0:19:18.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.32,0:19:18.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right
Dialogue: 1,0:19:18.17,0:19:20.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也能应付得来你的小小牛虫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.17,0:19:20.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I can handle your little bull worm too
Dialogue: 1,0:19:20.75,0:19:23.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为我最强
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.75,0:19:23.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cause I am the best there is
Dialogue: 1,0:19:23.00,0:19:24.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,根本没东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.00,0:19:24.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There ain't nothing
Dialogue: 1,0:19:24.03,0:19:26.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能又大又凶到我抓不住的地步
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.03,0:19:26.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,too big or too ornery for me to catch
Dialogue: 1,0:19:26.52,0:19:27.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.52,0:19:27.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 1,0:19:27.38,0:19:27.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.38,0:19:27.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say it
Dialogue: 1,0:19:28.14,0:19:28.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.14,0:19:28.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There isn't anything--
Dialogue: 1,0:19:29.17,0:19:30.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,根本没东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.17,0:19:30.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ain't nothing--
Dialogue: 1,0:19:30.44,0:19:33.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,根本没东西能又大又凶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.44,0:19:33.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ain't nothing too big or too ornery
Dialogue: 1,0:19:33.71,0:19:34.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到你抓不住的地步
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.71,0:19:34.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for you to catch
Dialogue: 1,0:19:34.77,0:19:35.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.77,0:19:35.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But--
Dialogue: 1,0:19:36.50,0:19:36.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.50,0:19:36.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But
Dialogue: 1,0:19:37.62,0:19:38.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.62,0:19:38.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And
Dialogue: 1,0:19:38.98,0:19:39.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.98,0:19:39.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We
Dialogue: 1,0:19:39.87,0:19:40.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,会死
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.87,0:19:40.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Die
Dialogue: 1,0:19:40.90,0:19:41.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.90,0:19:41.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah but
Dialogue: 1,0:19:41.85,0:19:42.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.85,0:19:42.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You see
Dialogue: 1,0:19:42.45,0:19:43.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.45,0:19:43.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:19:43.02,0:19:43.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,死掉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.02,0:19:43.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Die
Dialogue: 1,0:19:47.42,0:19:48.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虫来过的迹象
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.42,0:19:48.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Worm sign
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.42,0:19:48.95,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(842,920)}牌 子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.95,0:19:50.12,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(464,670)}虫子
Dialogue: 1,0:19:50.35,0:19:51.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它就在这洞里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.35,0:19:51.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's in that cave
Dialogue: 1,0:19:51.95,0:19:53.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪  你确定你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.95,0:19:53.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy are you sure you--
Dialogue: 1,0:19:53.22,0:19:54.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.22,0:19:54.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course I am
Dialogue: 1,0:19:54.20,0:19:55.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.20,0:19:55.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going in
Dialogue: 1,0:19:55.17,0:20:00.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不做一大盘炖虫子我绝不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.17,0:19:56.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I ain't coming out
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.71,0:20:00.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,until I got me a big heaping plate of worm stew
Dialogue: 1,0:20:04.70,0:20:07.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,找到你了  偷尾巴的害虫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.70,0:20:07.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There you are you tail nabbing varmit
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.92,0:20:14.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我快赢了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.92,0:20:14.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm winning Spongebob
Dialogue: 1,0:20:14.25,0:20:15.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪  那不是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.25,0:20:15.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy, that's not--
Dialogue: 1,0:20:19.79,0:20:21.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,应该不会太久的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.79,0:20:21.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This shouldn't take long
Dialogue: 1,0:20:21.15,0:20:22.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪  那不是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.15,0:20:22.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy, that's not--
Dialogue: 1,0:20:24.85,0:20:26.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.85,0:20:26.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Almost done
Dialogue: 1,0:20:26.17,0:20:27.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.17,0:20:27.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:20:30.93,0:20:32.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抓到它了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.93,0:20:32.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got him, Spongebob
Dialogue: 1,0:20:33.82,0:20:34.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.82,0:20:34.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:35.67,0:20:36.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.67,0:20:36.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boy howdy
Dialogue: 1,0:20:36.92,0:20:39.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这东西还挺不好打
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.92,0:20:39.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This critter put up some sort of fight
Dialogue: 1,0:20:39.20,0:20:40.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但我可是德克萨斯来的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.20,0:20:40.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I'm from Texas
Dialogue: 1,0:20:40.47,0:20:43.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你也能看得出来  没有虫子是我对手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.47,0:20:43.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And as you can see, no worm is a match for me
Dialogue: 1,0:20:43.45,0:20:44.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我连我尾巴都找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.45,0:20:44.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I even found my tail
Dialogue: 1,0:20:46.32,0:20:47.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那不是虫子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.32,0:20:47.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's not the worm
Dialogue: 1,0:20:48.05,0:20:48.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.05,0:20:48.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pardon?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:48.67,0:20:50.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那不是虫子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.67,0:20:50.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That not the worm
Dialogue: 1,0:20:50.38,0:20:51.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是虫子的舌头
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.38,0:20:51.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's his tongue
Dialogue: 1,0:20:59.54,0:21:01.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个是舌头
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.54,0:21:01.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is the tongue
Dialogue: 1,0:21:01.12,0:21:04.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这一整个才是虫子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.12,0:21:04.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and the whole thing is the worm--
Dialogue: 1,0:21:06.25,0:21:08.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快逃命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.25,0:21:08.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Run for your life
Dialogue: 1,0:21:17.26,0:21:18.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有什么计划  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.26,0:21:18.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So what the plan, Sandy?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:19.50,0:21:20.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跑快点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.50,0:21:20.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Run faster
Dialogue: 1,0:21:21.07,0:21:22.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我本来能想到的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.07,0:21:22.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I could have thought of that
Dialogue: 1,0:21:23.06,0:21:23.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.06,0:21:23.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute
Dialogue: 1,0:21:23.90,0:21:25.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我说的对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.90,0:21:25.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was right, wasn't I?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:25.77,0:21:26.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等会再说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.77,0:21:26.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Later
Dialogue: 1,0:21:27.08,0:21:28.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它太大  你抓不了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.08,0:21:28.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He is too big for you, isn't he?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:28.83,0:21:29.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在不是时候  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.83,0:21:29.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not now Spongebob
Dialogue: 1,0:21:30.10,0:21:31.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要听你说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.10,0:21:31.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want to hear you say it
Dialogue: 1,0:21:31.35,0:21:33.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能不能以后再说这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.35,0:21:33.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can we talk about this some other time?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:33.03,0:21:33.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.03,0:21:33.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say it
Dialogue: 1,0:21:33.72,0:21:34.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.72,0:21:34.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spongebob
Dialogue: 1,0:21:34.49,0:21:35.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不说我就绊倒你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.49,0:21:35.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say it or I'll trip you
Dialogue: 1,0:21:35.70,0:21:36.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.70,0:21:36.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:21:36.52,0:21:36.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别瞎说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.52,0:21:36.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get away
Dialogue: 1,0:21:36.90,0:21:37.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.90,0:21:37.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say it
Dialogue: 1,0:21:37.66,0:21:38.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还不是时候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.66,0:21:38.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not now
Dialogue: 1,0:21:38.31,0:21:38.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.31,0:21:38.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say it
Dialogue: 1,0:21:38.81,0:21:39.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.81,0:21:39.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 1,0:21:39.78,0:21:41.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你一直都对  我一直都错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.78,0:21:41.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You were right and I was wrong
Dialogue: 1,0:21:41.47,0:21:43.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一直错错错错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.47,0:21:43.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was wrong, wrong wrong, wrong
Dialogue: 1,0:21:43.45,0:21:44.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这下高兴了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.45,0:21:44.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you happy now?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:44.90,0:21:46.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.90,0:21:46.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I knew it
Dialogue: 1,0:22:04.98,0:22:06.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.98,0:22:06.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not again
Dialogue: 1,0:22:06.95,0:22:07.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.95,0:22:07.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:08.14,0:22:08.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.14,0:22:08.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:08.96,0:22:10.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.96,0:22:10.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do we do now?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:15.88,0:22:16.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.88,0:22:16.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got it
Dialogue: 1,0:22:16.71,0:22:18.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你还有回形针跟线头吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.71,0:22:17.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spongebob, you still got
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.73,0:22:18.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that paperclip and that string?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:19.20,0:22:20.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我早想到了  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.20,0:22:20.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm way ahead of you Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:22:22.05,0:22:22.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.05,0:22:22.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look
Dialogue: 1,0:22:22.70,0:22:23.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是个项链
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.70,0:22:23.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a necklace
Dialogue: 1,0:22:23.73,0:22:27.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,S表示海绵宝宝  也可以表示珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.73,0:22:27.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,S for Spongebob, or S for Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:22:27.50,0:22:29.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样我们遗体身份就清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.50,0:22:29.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That way they can identify our bodies
Dialogue: 1,0:22:30.22,0:22:31.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.22,0:22:31.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No silly
Dialogue: 1,0:22:31.53,0:22:33.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让这个S表示保命如何
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.53,0:22:33.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How about S for save our skins?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:41.02,0:22:43.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样才叫牛仔表演
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.02,0:22:43.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now this is what I call a rodeo
Dialogue: 1,0:22:43.40,0:22:45.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,待在上面就能平安无事了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.40,0:22:45.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll be nice and safe up here
Dialogue: 1,0:23:00.90,0:23:02.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.90,0:23:02.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We did it
Dialogue: 1,0:23:02.86,0:23:04.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这下它出不来了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.86,0:23:04.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He'll never get out of there
Dialogue: 1,0:23:04.22,0:23:05.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们拯救了裤头村
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.22,0:23:05.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We saved the town
Dialogue: 1,0:23:06.45,0:23:08.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去跟大家报喜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.45,0:23:08.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's go tell everybody
Dialogue: 1,0:23:08.70,0:23:09.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,推
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.70,0:23:09.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Push
Dialogue: 1,0:23:12.19,0:23:13.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,推
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.19,0:23:13.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Push
